{
  "stem": "6719.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She hated Jews like there was no tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But at the time, she couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But when Hitler came in, she, uh, apparently went to the authorities, uh, about my father.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Ah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what happened was that, uh, apparently he, uh-- I was arrested first, before he was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In hiding.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was arrested too, but he was let-- you see, that-- that-- that-- there's something that-- one should never put a label on people, but sometimes, it just happens.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Uh, the Viennese are a very funny, funny people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Uh, there were a lot of Nazis that weren't Nazis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were Nazis.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe they were afraid, or maybe they-- they saw some gain by becoming Nazis.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father knew a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he knew a lot of people in the police department.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I think that due to the fact-- I think, I'm not sure-- that due to the fact of this what one would call connection, he was later on released and came home.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Uh, he was, uh, incarcerated in a place called [NON-ENGLISH], which means the main court building, in-- in-- in-- I think it's the 9th district that this was in.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, uh, I was picked up and, uh, you know, the-- the-- the-- the period of-- [SIGHS].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "First of all, I found out later that most of the people that were arrested in March and were sent to a concentration camp were sent to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This I found out later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "How the hell I ended up in Buchenwald, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "19-- that's right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was in 1938.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, uh, uh--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "14.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that's-- that's-- that's the thing that-- and you know what?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have-- I thought about it again this morning, OK?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
